  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What's this, boy?",
      "zh": "這是什麼，孩子？",
      "ja": "これは何だい、坊や？",
      "time": "00:00:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Whoa!",
      "zh": "哇！",
      "ja": "おおっ！",
      "time": "00:00:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Still in there, isn't it?",
      "zh": "還在裡面，對吧？",
      "ja": "まだ中にあるね？",
      "time": "00:00:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yep.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:00:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Here we go.",
      "zh": "我們開始吧。",
      "ja": "さあ、行こう。",
      "time": "00:00:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Over here.",
      "zh": "這邊。",
      "ja": "こっちだ。",
      "time": "00:00:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let's get to the ropes.",
      "zh": "我們去繩索那裡。",
      "ja": "ロープのところへ行こう。",
      "time": "00:00:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ready?",
      "zh": "準備好了嗎？",
      "ja": "準備はいい？",
      "time": "00:01:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Your first.",
      "zh": "你先。",
      "ja": "君からだ。",
      "time": "00:01:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Scared.",
      "zh": "害怕了。",
      "ja": "怖い。",
      "time": "00:01:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "So off.",
      "zh": "那就出發吧。",
      "ja": "じゃあ、行くぞ。",
      "time": "00:01:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "How close?",
      "zh": "有多近？",
      "ja": "どれくらい近い？",
      "time": "00:01:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Nope, this will slow down.",
      "zh": "不會，這會慢下來。",
      "ja": "いや、これは減速する。",
      "time": "00:01:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let's go.",
      "zh": "走吧。",
      "ja": "行こう。",
      "time": "00:01:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Whoa!",
      "zh": "哇！",
      "ja": "おおっ！",
      "time": "00:01:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Well, this is it.",
      "zh": "好了，就是這裡。",
      "ja": "さて、ここだ。",
      "time": "00:01:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Where?",
      "zh": "在哪裡？",
      "ja": "どこ？",
      "time": "00:01:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It should be somewhere on the cable.",
      "zh": "應該在纜繩上的某處。",
      "ja": "ケーブルのどこかにあるはずだ。",
      "time": "00:01:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'll start over here.",
      "zh": "我從這邊開始。",
      "ja": "こっちから始めるよ。",
      "time": "00:01:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay, I'll take this side.",
      "zh": "好，我負責這邊。",
      "ja": "わかった、こっちを担当する。",
      "time": "00:01:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Shane.",
      "zh": "Shane。",
      "ja": "シェーン。",
      "time": "00:01:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Is that?",
      "zh": "那是？",
      "ja": "あれは？",
      "time": "00:01:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That's it.",
      "zh": "就是它。",
      "ja": "それだ。",
      "time": "00:02:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That's it.",
      "zh": "就是它。",
      "ja": "それだ。",
      "time": "00:02:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You found it.",
      "zh": "你找到了。",
      "ja": "見つけたね。",
      "time": "00:02:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We found it.",
      "zh": "我們找到了。",
      "ja": "見つけたよ。",
      "time": "00:02:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "See you there.",
      "zh": "那裡見。",
      "ja": "そこで会おう。",
      "time": "00:02:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:02:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:02:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Is this them?",
      "zh": "這是他們嗎？",
      "ja": "これが彼ら？",
      "time": "00:02:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Really, is this?",
      "zh": "真的嗎，這是？",
      "ja": "本当にこれ？",
      "time": "00:02:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Well, they have the map now.",
      "zh": "嗯，他們現在有地圖了。",
      "ja": "まあ、彼らは今地図を持っている。",
      "time": "00:02:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That's the end of the story, though.",
      "zh": "不過故事就到這裡結束了。",
      "ja": "でもこれが物語の終わりだ。",
      "time": "00:02:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:02:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Well, I imagined some sort of ending.",
      "zh": "我想像了一個結局。",
      "ja": "まあ、何かしらの結末を想像してた。",
      "time": "00:02:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But this is a happy ending.",
      "zh": "但這是個快樂的結局。",
      "ja": "でもこれはハッピーエンドだ。",
      "time": "00:02:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "They fell on the map.",
      "zh": "他們跌在地圖上。",
      "ja": "彼らは地図の上に落ちた。",
      "time": "00:02:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And now onto the next book of my series,",
      "zh": "現在進入我系列的下一本書，",
      "ja": "そして今、私のシリーズの次の本へ、",
      "time": "00:02:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "where they'll use it to find the artifact.",
      "zh": "他們將用它來尋找神器。",
      "ja": "彼らはそれを使って遺物を探す。",
      "time": "00:02:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What about Shane and Sabrina's relationship, though?",
      "zh": "不過Shane和Sabrina的關係呢？",
      "ja": "でもシェーンとサブリナの関係は？",
      "time": "00:02:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The romance?",
      "zh": "浪漫情節？",
      "ja": "ロマンス？",
      "time": "00:02:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Romance doesn't really fit in my books.",
      "zh": "浪漫不太適合我的書。",
      "ja": "ロマンスは私の本にはあまり合わない。",
      "time": "00:02:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I know Mr. Action Adventure, but that doesn't mean you can't have",
      "zh": "我知道你是動作冒險先生，但這不代表你不能有",
      "ja": "アクションアドベンチャーの先生だけど、それはロマンスがあってはいけないってことじゃない。",
      "time": "00:02:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "some romance in it.",
      "zh": "一些浪漫情節。",
      "ja": "少しのロマンスを入れてもいい。",
      "time": "00:02:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "They should at least hug and share a long look.",
      "zh": "他們至少應該擁抱並深情對望。",
      "ja": "少なくともハグして長い視線を交わすべきだ。",
      "time": "00:02:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Or maybe even a kiss?",
      "zh": "或者甚至親吻？",
      "ja": "あるいはキスも？",
      "time": "00:02:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Seriously, Mackenzie, I need your help on this.",
      "zh": "說真的，Mackenzie，我需要你的幫助。",
      "ja": "本気で、マッケンジー、これについて助けてほしい。",
      "time": "00:02:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay, what did you think overall?",
      "zh": "好，你整體覺得怎麼樣？",
      "ja": "じゃあ、全体的にどう思った？",
      "time": "00:02:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I like it.",
      "zh": "我喜歡。",
      "ja": "好きだよ。",
      "time": "00:02:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The villain seems a little over the top, and I don't always get his motivation.",
      "zh": "反派有點誇張，我不太明白他的動機。",
      "ja": "悪役がちょっと大げさで、動機がよくわからない。",
      "time": "00:02:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Good.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "いいね。",
      "time": "00:03:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What else?",
      "zh": "還有呢？",
      "ja": "他には？",
      "time": "00:03:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I like the chemistry between Shane and Sabrina,",
      "zh": "我喜歡Shane和Sabrina之間的化學反應，",
      "ja": "シェーンとサブリナのケミストリーが好きだ。",
      "time": "00:03:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "but I really do think they have a relationship that could be",
      "zh": "但我真的覺得他們的關係可以",
      "ja": "でも彼らの関係はもっと発展できると思う。",
      "time": "00:03:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "developed into something more hard.",
      "zh": "發展成更深的東西。",
      "ja": "もっと深いものに発展できる。",
      "time": "00:03:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Doly noted.",
      "zh": "已記下。",
      "ja": "了解した。",
      "time": "00:03:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You're not going to do anything about that, are you?",
      "zh": "你不打算做點什麼吧？",
      "ja": "それについて何かするつもりはないよね？",
      "time": "00:03:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No.",
      "zh": "不會。",
      "ja": "いや。",
      "time": "00:03:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But thank you for reading my latest.",
      "zh": "但謝謝你讀我的最新作品。",
      "ja": "でも、私の最新作を読んでくれてありがとう。",
      "time": "00:03:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You're the best.",
      "zh": "你是最棒的。",
      "ja": "君は最高だ。",
      "time": "00:03:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Happy to.",
      "zh": "樂意。",
      "ja": "喜んで。",
      "time": "00:03:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And my compensation?",
      "zh": "那我的報酬呢？",
      "ja": "それで、報酬は？",
      "time": "00:03:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh.",
      "zh": "喔。",
      "ja": "ああ。",
      "time": "00:03:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Just in time.",
      "zh": "正好。",
      "ja": "ちょうどいいタイミング。",
      "time": "00:03:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's a good bake, I think.",
      "zh": "我覺得這蛋糕不錯。",
      "ja": "いい焼き菓子だと思う。",
      "time": "00:03:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Heavenly.",
      "zh": "美味極了。",
      "ja": "天国の味だ。",
      "time": "00:03:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You know I've offered to teach you how to make this, like,",
      "zh": "你知道我已經提議教你怎麼做這個，像是，",
      "ja": "これの作り方を教えてあげるって、もう何度も言ったよね、",
      "time": "00:03:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "20 times by now, right?",
      "zh": "現在已經20次了，對吧？",
      "ja": "もう20回くらいは言ったよね？",
      "time": "00:03:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I say why bother learning when you can.",
      "zh": "我說既然可以依賴你，何必學呢。",
      "ja": "頼れるなら、わざわざ覚える必要ないよ。",
      "time": "00:03:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "When you could be dependent on me, I know.",
      "zh": "你可以依賴我，我知道。",
      "ja": "僕に頼ればいいんだよね、わかってる。",
      "time": "00:03:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You're dependent on my opinion of your books,",
      "zh": "你依賴我對你書的看法，",
      "ja": "君は僕の本の評価に依存してる。",
      "time": "00:03:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "so I was morally job security.",
      "zh": "所以我算是道德上的工作保障。",
      "ja": "だから僕は道徳的な雇用保障だね。",
      "time": "00:03:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But you really like the book, though?",
      "zh": "但你真的喜歡這本書嗎？",
      "ja": "でも本当に本は好き？",
      "time": "00:03:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:03:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You doubt me every time.",
      "zh": "你每次都懷疑我。",
      "ja": "君はいつも僕を疑う。",
      "time": "00:03:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I don't rule number one of feedback,",
      "zh": "我不遵守反饋的第一條規則，",
      "ja": "フィードバックの第一ルールを守ってない。",
      "time": "00:03:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "because you don't ask your friends.",
      "zh": "因為你不問你的朋友。",
      "ja": "友達に聞かないから。",
      "time": "00:03:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But you do, because I'm always honest with you.",
      "zh": "但你會問，因為我總是對你誠實。",
      "ja": "でも君は聞く、僕はいつも正直だから。",
      "time": "00:03:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Even brutal at time.",
      "zh": "有時甚至很殘酷。",
      "ja": "時には厳しいこともあるけど。",
      "time": "00:03:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Well, now I just have to brace myself for my editor.",
      "zh": "好吧，現在我得準備面對我的編輯了。",
      "ja": "さて、今度は編集者に備えなきゃ。",
      "time": "00:03:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It'll be fine.",
      "zh": "會沒事的。",
      "ja": "大丈夫だよ。",
      "time": "00:04:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It always is.",
      "zh": "總是這樣。",
      "ja": "いつもそうだ。",
      "time": "00:04:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "So, anything cool going on at work?",
      "zh": "那麼，工作上有什麼酷的事嗎？",
      "ja": "で、仕事で何か面白いことあった？",
      "time": "00:04:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Nothing like adventures to the jungle,",
      "zh": "沒有像叢林冒險那樣的事，",
      "ja": "ジャングルへの冒険みたいなことはないけど、",
      "time": "00:04:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "till I hit my mouth.",
      "zh": "直到我嘴巴受傷。",
      "ja": "口を打つまではね。",
      "time": "00:04:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No.",
      "zh": "沒有。",
      "ja": "いや。",
      "time": "00:04:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Come on, you have the ultimate dream job",
      "zh": "拜託，你有終極夢想工作",
      "ja": "さあ、君は最高の夢の仕事を持ってるんだ。",
      "time": "00:04:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "working at a candy company.",
      "zh": "在糖果公司工作。",
      "ja": "キャンディ会社で働いてる。",
      "time": "00:04:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Chocolate.",
      "zh": "巧克力。",
      "ja": "チョコレート。",
      "time": "00:04:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You better.",
      "zh": "你最好是。",
      "ja": "そうだろうね。",
      "time": "00:04:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Doesn't necessarily mean it's exciting.",
      "zh": "不一定代表很刺激。",
      "ja": "必ずしも刺激的とは限らない。",
      "time": "00:04:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "All right, whatever happened to that new guy you talked",
      "zh": "好吧，你說過的那個新男孩怎麼樣了",
      "ja": "さて、君が話してた新しい男の子はどうなった？",
      "time": "00:04:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "about.",
      "zh": "呢？",
      "ja": "って？",
      "time": "00:04:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The floor manager.",
      "zh": "樓層經理。",
      "ja": "フロアマネージャー。",
      "time": "00:04:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "zh": "沒什麼。",
      "ja": "特にない。",
      "time": "00:04:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's just a new face.",
      "zh": "只是個新面孔。",
      "ja": "ただの新しい顔だ。",
      "time": "00:04:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maybe you should talk to him.",
      "zh": "也許你應該跟他聊聊。",
      "ja": "彼と話してみたら？",
      "time": "00:04:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm really not interested in him.",
      "zh": "我真的對他沒興趣。",
      "ja": "僕は彼に全然興味ない。",
      "time": "00:04:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Or an office from his.",
      "zh": "或者他辦公室的人。",
      "ja": "あるいは彼のオフィスの人。",
      "time": "00:04:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
